# Changelog

## [0.4.3]
### Added
- (RemoteMethodDirective): add setParameter Method

## [0.4.2]
### Fixed
- (BaseHttpRemoteMethod): encode the url path params

## [0.4.1]
### Fixed
- add missing peer deps

## [0.4.0]
### Changed
- (RemoteMethodDirective): expose remote method execution errors

## [0.3.17]
### Changed
- (schematics): modularise the directive creation

## [0.3.16]
### Fixed
- (RemoteMethodTemplate*Directive): add support for remote methods without parameters

## [0.3.15]
### Fixed
- (RemoteMethodTemplateCollectionDirective): use the private member to access the remote method token

## [0.3.14]
### Added
- (RemoteMethodTemplateCollectionDirective): add trackBy support
### Fixed
- (schematics): export path creation

## [0.3.13]
### Added
- (schematics): add the directive schematic
### Fixed
- (RxapRemoteMethod): add string or metadata support

## [0.3.12]
### Fixed
- (RemoteMethodTemplate*Directive): change the renderTemplate method scope to public

## [0.3.11]
### Changed
- Allow remote method directive extension

## [0.3.10]
### Added
- Allow to pause auto refresh and manuel trigger refresh

## [0.3.9]
### Changed
- (*HttpRemoteMethod) add support for retry and timeout

## [0.3.8]
### Changed
- optional injector property
- use utility type

## [0.3.7]
### Added
- ProxyRemoteMethod

## [0.3.6]
### Added
- RemoteMethodTemplateDirective
- RemoteMethodTemplateCollectionDirective

## [0.3.5]
### Added
- BaseHttpRemoteMethod

## [0.3.4]
### Added
- ng-update support

## [0.3.3]
### Changed
- replace the @rxap/loader with @rxap/definition

## [0.3.2]

### Added
- Contenteditable directive

## [0.3.1]

### Added
- support for the new rxapConfirm directive

### Changed
- the _call method can by sync
- the RemoteMethodLoader accepts a string, instance or injection token

## [0.3.0]

Package initialisation
